        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Neocepolis spp. from Vietnam, radula: A–C. N. merarcha (CUMZ 2551); (D–F) N. morleti (CUMZ 2553). (A, D) Central tooth with the first to the second lateral teeth; (B, E) lateral teeth with the tricuspid marginal teeth transition; (C, F) outermost marginal teeth. Numbers indicate order of lateral and marginal teeth. Central tooth indicated by ‘‘C’’." ;
